				<td colspan="2"><span>At the risk of sounding like a total jerk, I say accidental exp death is a part of pvp. I play on Tallon Zek and we talk smack and treat each other so poorly that you'd think if we met in real life we'd slit each other's throats. LOL! 
<br />

<br />
We act like this because we enjoy it, not because we truly hate one another. Theres no better feeling in the world than taking someone down that has killed/taunted you in the past and sending them a tell saying &quot;remember me @#^$%?&quot;
<br />

<br />
A lot of people that come from a blue server to try out a zek are appalled. They call us children for our foul language and behavior. Sure I'll call you horrible, blasphemous things when you kill me in the middle of a quad-kite, but if I saw you the next day in real life I'd shake your hand and say &quot;good job you evil bastard.&quot;
