				<td colspan="2"><span>Exp deaths happen, especially on a PvP server in zones filled with yard trash mobs (that I am very happy to kite when I can, I might add) that will hit you for insanely high damage.  The higher in level you get, the more you start to realize the inevitability of this fact. 
<br />

